---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What I am doing now. 最近在做什么。" path="/now">
  <section class="shell" style="padding: 48px 0 96px;">
    <div style="max-width: 760px;">
      <p class="mono" style="color: var(--warm); font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 14px;">NOW / 近况</p>
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 0.96; margin: 0 0 24px;">Now</h1>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>This is my <strong>/now</strong> page, inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com">nownownow.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Right now, I am focused on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Building this personal site. 搭建自己的小空间。</li>
          <li>Trying new web tools.</li>
          <li>Writing down ideas before they disappear.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Last updated: June 2026.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
